<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"/></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td style="background-color:#2E86C1;height:5px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background-color:#E87722;height:3px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;">
<tr>
<td style="padding:20px 40px;">
<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgy7mvhnm/image/upload/w_200,h_80,c_fit/v1773805978/talentforce_logo_header_4k_wmbyal.png" height="60" alt="TalentForce Recruit" style="display:block;"/>
</td>
<td align="right" style="padding:20px 40px;font-size:11px;color:#999999;white-space:nowrap;">
Recruitment Notification
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#2E86C1;">
<tr><td style="padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;">
<h1 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:26px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold;">Welcome to TalentForce!</h1>
<p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#d6eaf8;">Your candidate portal access is ready</p>
</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td style="background-color:#E87722;height:4px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;">
<tr><td style="padding:36px 40px;">

<p style="font-size:15px;color:#2c2c2c;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;">
Dear <strong>{!Contact.FirstName} {!Contact.LastName}</strong>,
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px;color:#2c2c2c;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;">
Your application has been reviewed and you have been granted access to the 
<strong>TalentForce Recruit</strong> candidate portal. You can now log in to 
track your application status in real time.
</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-left:4px solid #2E86C1;background-color:#f4f8fd;margin-bottom:24px;">
<tr><td style="padding:18px 22px;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td style="padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8f5;font-size:13px;color:#888888;width:180px;">Username</td>
<td style="padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8f5;font-size:13px;color:#2c2c2c;font-weight:bold;">{!Contact.Email}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:9px 0;font-size:13px;color:#888888;">Portal Access</td>
<td style="padding:9px 0;font-size:13px;color:#2c2c2c;font-weight:bold;">TalentForce Candidate Portal</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-left:4px solid #E87722;background-color:#fff8f0;margin-bottom:28px;">
<tr><td style="padding:14px 18px;">
<p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#7a4a00;line-height:1.7;">
<strong>Next step:</strong> Click the button below to set your password and activate your account. 
This link is valid for 24 hours.
</p>
</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:28px;">
<tr><td align="center">
<a href="{!Community.ResetPasswordUrl}" 
   style="display:inline-block;background-color:#2E86C1;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;padding:14px 40px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;">
   Set My Password &amp; Login
</a>
</td></tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size:14px;color:#2c2c2c;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;">
If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br/>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:#2E86C1;">{!Community.ResetPasswordUrl}</span>
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px;color:#2c2c2c;line-height:1.7;margin:28px 0 0 0;">
Kind regards,<br/>
<strong style="color:#2E86C1;">TalentForce Recruit</strong><br/>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:#999999;">Recruitment Team</span>
</p>

</td></tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;">
<tr>
<td style="padding:16px 40px;font-size:11px;color:#aaaaaa;">This email is confidential and intended solely for the named recipient.</td>
<td align="right" style="padding:16px 40px;font-size:11px;color:#E87722;font-weight:bold;white-space:nowrap;">TalentForce Recruit</td>
</tr>
</table>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td style="background-color:#E87722;height:3px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background-color:#2E86C1;height:5px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&#160;</td></tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>